      <title>特朗普的新关税持有汽车制造商的股票，欧洲股票下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/european-stock-futures-drop-trump-s-auto-tariffs-dent-sentiment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）宣布对汽车进口的25％关税之后，欧洲股票下跌，更新他的贸易政策将损害公司收入和经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/european-stock-futures-drop-trump-s-auto-tariffs-dent-sentiment</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 06:57:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>洛里金德（Robinhood）超越模因股票，想成为您的银行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/robinhood-moving-beyond-meme-stocks-now-wants-to-be-your-bank</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Robinhood Markets Inc.已超越了其模因时代，成为所有条纹散户投资者的首选平台 - 加密狂热者，新手金融家和精致的投机者。现在，它将它更进一步：它也想成为您的银行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/robinhood-moving-beyond-meme-stocks-now-wants-to-be-your-bank</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 01:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股票随着贸易云的经济前景而下降：市场包裹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国推动对汽车制造商的关税提前，股票下跌，这加剧了人们对扩大贸易战争的担忧，该战争的数据超过了显示世界上最大经济体增长速度快的速度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 22:44:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
